snippet.title: Geek Protagonist
snippet.description: Hello. This channel is gonna be for geeks and nerds culture mainly with a some sprinkles of reality. Sometimes you may hear me have a deep thought about a situation. Other times just having a chat. Giving my opinion.I'll be doing reviews on  comics, movies and such some unlockings. It'll be fun and also a little insight into how I see things and maybe we'll see them together. We may and will disagree on things but at the end of the day it's all fun.  Please like comment subscribe and share. I really do appreciate you going on this journey with me. I wish you all good tidings.
